{
  "stem": "12402.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's a reason.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, with us, if they-- we had our papers already, and they had their own papers, so there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They checked it and it was OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went through especially the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived to the city of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a concentration camp-- not concentration like us, but the concentration to keep all the workers-- Russian, Ukraine, Polish, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They kept them concentrated to ship them off to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got there, so this Malzman said, uh oh, I have a problem.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw a policeman which he knows me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, with-- there was no Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Finished.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I've got to get out of here as fast as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The minute there'll be an opening, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Course, they took to a factory, they took to factory for work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Myself, I didn't want to go to a factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I don't want to go-- I want to go on the farm like my brother who was sick after the typhoid.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to the examination afterwards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so-- so what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were-- this Malzman got a job right away, went to a-- he said, I don't care where I get as long getting it out of here because here I get caught right away.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, his-- this woman was with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took her afterwards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going to forget about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He maybe six month-- we were in Germany when he-- he organized for her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was still in the hole there, and she went to [INAUDIBLE], she got shot in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After the war we found out.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
